 Joining Attributes<body>

  Joining Attributes  
      Useful if there are interactions among attributes
 
     Estimates of probabilitiesroblem-
 
   Given: Set of       {age, weight, height, shoe-size}
  Find: Attribute      {age, height, weight}
  Such that accuracy of classifier is maximized
       Partition Selection Problem-
 
   Given: Set of independent      {{age}, {weight}, {height}, {shoe-size}}
  Find: Attribute      {{age, height}, {weight}}
  Such that accuracy of classifier is maximized       
 
